---
---
<section id="experiencia" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-bg-secondary relative">
  <!-- Sutil resplandor de fondo -->
  <div class="absolute left-0 top-1/4 w-[35vw] h-[35vw] bg-accent-glow/5 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
    <!-- Header de sección -->
    <div class="reveal text-center mb-20">
      <span class="font-mono text-xs text-accent uppercase tracking-widest block mb-3">Experiencia</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white mb-4">Trayectoria profesional</h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary max-w-xl mx-auto text-base md:text-lg">Mi recorrido profesional en empresas tecnológicas líderes del sector.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Lista de experiencia -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto flex flex-col gap-6">
      
      <!-- Experiencia 1: TechCorp Solutions -->
      <div class="reveal group border-b border-border-custom last:border-b-0 pb-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:pl-4">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-12">
          <!-- Columna Izquierda: Periodo -->
          <div class="md:w-44 shrink-0 flex flex-col">
            <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-accent tracking-wider group-hover:text-accent-secondary transition-colors">2023 - Presente</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1 uppercase tracking-widest">1 año +</span>
          </div>

          <!-- Columna Derecha: Contenido -->
          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col gap-4">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-300">Senior Software Engineer</h3>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium text-text-secondary mt-0.5">TechCorp Solutions — Madrid, España</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Logros -->
            <ul class="list-none flex flex-col gap-2.5">
              <li class="relative pl-6 text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed before:content-['▹'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-accent before:font-bold">
                Liderazgo técnico de un equipo de 8 desarrolladores en el rediseño de la plataforma principal.
              </li>
              <li class="relative pl-6 text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed before:content-['▹'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-accent before:font-bold">
                Implementación de arquitectura de microservicios reduciendo latencia en un 40%.
              </li>
              <li class="relative pl-6 text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed before:content-['▹'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-accent before:font-bold">
                Diseño e implementación de pipelines CI/CD con GitHub Actions y Kubernetes.
              </li>
              <li class="relative pl-6 text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed before:content-['▹'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-accent before:font-bold">
                Mentoría a desarrolladores junior y code reviews del equipo.
              </li>
            </ul>

            <!-- Tags -->
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-2">
              <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-text-muted px-2.5 py-1 bg-bg-primary border border-border-custom rounded hover:border-accent/30 cursor-default transition-all duration-300">React</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-text-muted px-2.5 py-1 bg-bg-primary border border-border-custom rounded hover:border-accent/30 cursor-default transition-all duration-300">Go</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-text-muted px-2.5 py-1 bg-bg-primary border border-border-custom rounded hover:border-accent/30 cursor-default transition-all duration-300">Kubernetes</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-text-muted px-2.5 py-1 bg-bg-primary border border-border-custom rounded hover:border-accent/30 cursor-default transition-all duration-300">AWS</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-text-muted px-2.5 py-1 bg-bg-primary border border-border-custom rounded hover:border-accent/30 cursor-default transition-all duration-300">gRPC</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Experiencia 2: DataFlow Analytics -->
      <div class="reveal group border-b border-border-custom last:border-b-0 pb-8 pt-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:pl-4">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-12">
          <!-- Columna Izquierda: Periodo -->
          <div class="md:w-44 shrink-0 flex flex-col">
            <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-accent tracking-wider group-hover:text-accent-secondary transition-colors">2021 - 2023</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1 uppercase tracking-widest">2 años</span>
          </div>

          <!-- Columna Derecha: Contenido -->
          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col gap-4">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-300">Full Stack Developer</h3>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium text-text-secondary mt-0.5">DataFlow Analytics — Barcelona, España</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Logros -->
            <ul class="list-none flex flex-col gap-2.5">
              <li class="relative pl-6 text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed before:content-['▹'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-accent before:font-bold">
                Desarrollo de dashboards de análisis de datos en tiempo real con React y D3.js.
              </li>
              <li class="relative pl-6 text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed before:content-['▹'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-accent before:font-bold">
                Construcción de APIs RESTful y GraphQL con Node.js y TypeScript.
              </li>
              <li class="relative pl-6 text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed before:content-['▹'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-accent before:font-bold">
                Migración de base de datos MongoDB a PostgreSQL mejorando rendimiento en consultas complejas.
              </li>
              <li class="relative pl-6 text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed before:content-['▹'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-accent before:font-bold">
                Implementación de sistema de autenticación con OAuth2 y JWT.
              </li>
            </ul>

            <!-- Tags -->
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-2">
              <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-text-muted px-2.5 py-1 bg-bg-primary border border-border-custom rounded hover:border-accent/30 cursor-default transition-all duration-300">React</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-text-muted px-2.5 py-1 bg-bg-primary border border-border-custom rounded hover:border-accent/30 cursor-default transition-all duration-300">Node.js</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-text-muted px-2.5 py-1 bg-bg-primary border border-border-custom rounded hover:border-accent/30 cursor-default transition-all duration-300">PostgreSQL</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-text-muted px-2.5 py-1 bg-bg-primary border border-border-custom rounded hover:border-accent/30 cursor-default transition-all duration-300">Docker</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-text-muted px-2.5 py-1 bg-bg-primary border border-border-custom rounded hover:border-accent/30 cursor-default transition-all duration-300">GraphQL</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Experiencia 3: StartupHub -->
      <div class="reveal group border-b border-border-custom last:border-b-0 pb-8 pt-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:pl-4">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-12">
          <!-- Columna Izquierda: Periodo -->
          <div class="md:w-44 shrink-0 flex flex-col">
            <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-accent tracking-wider group-hover:text-accent-secondary transition-colors">2019 - 2021</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1 uppercase tracking-widest">2 años</span>
          </div>

          <!-- Columna Derecha: Contenido -->
          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col gap-4">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-300">Junior Software Developer</h3>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium text-text-secondary mt-0.5">StartupHub — Valencia, España</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Logros -->
            <ul class="list-none flex flex-col gap-2.5">
              <li class="relative pl-6 text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed before:content-['▹'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-accent before:font-bold">
                Desarrollo frontend de aplicaciones web para clientes del sector fintech.
              </li>
              <li class="relative pl-6 text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed before:content-['▹'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-accent before:font-bold">
                Colaboración en el desarrollo de una plataforma de pagos online procesando +10K transacciones diarias.
              </li>
              <li class="relative pl-6 text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed before:content-['▹'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-accent before:font-bold">
                Implementación de tests unitarios y de integración, alcanzando 85% de cobertura.
              </li>
              <li class="relative pl-6 text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed before:content-['▹'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-accent before:font-bold">
                Participación en sprints ágiles con metodologías Scrum.
              </li>
            </ul>

            <!-- Tags -->
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-2">
              <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-text-muted px-2.5 py-1 bg-bg-primary border border-border-custom rounded hover:border-accent/30 cursor-default transition-all duration-300">JavaScript</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-text-muted px-2.5 py-1 bg-bg-primary border border-border-custom rounded hover:border-accent/30 cursor-default transition-all duration-300">Vue.js</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-text-muted px-2.5 py-1 bg-bg-primary border border-border-custom rounded hover:border-accent/30 cursor-default transition-all duration-300">Python</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-text-muted px-2.5 py-1 bg-bg-primary border border-border-custom rounded hover:border-accent/30 cursor-default transition-all duration-300">MongoDB</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-text-muted px-2.5 py-1 bg-bg-primary border border-border-custom rounded hover:border-accent/30 cursor-default transition-all duration-300">Jest</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
